      <blockquote class="small">
        <p>Dan is the most exceptional Team Lead I've had the privilege of working with. Not only were they equally invested in project management priorities and practices, they worked hard to ensure our processes were effectively executed on by our engineering team. (Their retros are the best after mine!) Whenever our project load exceeded our team's capacity, I could trust that projects Dan managed would go as smoothly as those my team managed.</p>
