        <p>What makes Dan special isn't their keen design eye, their attention to detail, or their engineering prowess. You will find loads of folks that have all three… and Dan is indeed among the best I've seen.</p>
        <p>No. What makes Dan so special is their ability to understand people. Their sensitivity in this regard is their super power. They pick up on things others simply miss. They see the forest through the trees, while keeping their projects and teams moving in the right direction. Their sensitivity to others makes all the difference.</p>
        <p>I never once had to worry about the assignments I gave them, no matter how big and ambitious they might've been. Dan always delivered. That they'd do it while making you smile, well that was the just icing on the cake.</p>
