        <p>One of their super powers is the ability to get to the root of the issue and provide intelligent design that brings value to both clients and users. I've seen them help and guide designers into smarter designs; designs that place heavy importance on user experience, performance, and accessibility.</p>
        <p>Aside from their skills as a designer, they've got a stunning appreciation for all types of music. Not to mention they're hilarious. Truly an asset to any company in terms of skills and culture.</p>
