        <p>Dan is the best web designer that I've had the privilege to work with, which I don't say lightly. They not only have a fantastic aesthetic sense for design, but also grasps technology in a way that goes far beyond the visual and truly accounts for the fluidity of the web. When many sites mocked up in Photoshop are breaking because of a new device or extra-long piece of content, Dan's are adapting gracefully because they thought ahead.</p>
